X-Posting - https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C01DJ7QDC2H/p1730711534726409
A  Grafana version with a dashboards bug ended up in the AIHub `24.44.0 release`. While the PR that introduced issue has been reverted, some AIHub environments in SaaS ended up running this version.
For SaaS AIHub tenants, please use the Central Grafana instance: https://grafana.observability.instabase.com/

If youâ€™re facing issue with Grafana in sandbox environments, you can update Grafana from the master branch or the 22.44 release branch. Please reach out if still facing the issue.
